route = Route(pattern, mock_handler)
match = route.match(url)
assert match is not None
assert match.values == expected_values
pytest.mark.parametrize('pattern,url,expected_values', [(b'/foo/:id',
    b'/foo/123', {'id': '123'}), (b'/foo/:id/ufo/:b', b'/foo/223/ufo/a13',
    {'id': '223', 'b': 'a13'}), (b'/foo/:id/ufo/:b', b'/Foo/223/Ufo/a13', {
    'id': '223', 'b': 'a13'}), (b'/:a', b'/Something', {'a': 'Something'}),
    (b'/alive', b'/alive', None)])
